{"tid":319610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"琴日中午叫左個餐蛋飯食,比人恥笑","createTime":"2017-07-13T02:47:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T07:14:54.000Z","uid":25345,"like":451,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a74e3fdee2eb138f330a3d2221b21ee5d91e618e","tid":319610,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T02:47:24.000Z","msg":"係茶記叫左個餐蛋飯,跟住對面有兩個人搭檯<br />\n兩個係度諗食乜,其中一個想叫餐蛋飯,另一個就屌鬼佢,最on9就係食餐蛋飯<br />\n自己整好過啦咁,咁就冇叫<br />\n之後茶仔就放左碟餐蛋飯係我面前<br />\n我望下對面,佢又冇左我兩眼<br />\n之後就沈默左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbe432ab594b8310953331e28e740b6acf82fa1d","tid":319610,"uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:10:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b0bfd6a2f05ad15ae4d51ba2e0cc82f03705c47","tid":319610,"uid":81139,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T06:13:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係茶記叫左個餐蛋飯,跟住對面有兩個人搭檯<br />\n兩個係度諗食乜,其中一個想叫餐蛋飯,另一個就屌鬼佢,最on9就係食餐蛋飯<br />\n自己整好過啦咁,咁就冇叫<br />\n之後茶仔就放左碟餐蛋飯係我面前<br />\n我望下對面,佢又冇左我兩眼<br />\n之後就沈默左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地冇心恥笑你嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"725a2556809ebf991c33ebc57026f296df49b3d5","tid":319610,"uid":57787,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T06:57:14.000Z","msg":"啱啱食完餐蛋飯先睇到你依個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff602d3265e6302f7a73ef0ccd84438f864bc9e5","tid":319610,"uid":427,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T07:01:06.000Z","msg":"笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90925f5aad887749b973748fd2279974e4d74c6e","tid":319610,"uid":26003,"like":94,"dislike":2,"score":92,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T07:02:47.000Z","msg":"我係你就成程一路食飯一路望實佢地，<br />\n等佢地唔敢講抬起頭食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05611ff0f0a745fa6ce7ecec8c538a48047ad5a7","tid":319610,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T07:04:36.000Z","msg":"諗起中大CC can 特價飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ee2e3c04a080d1d9f3be44bea0de60629f46c4","tid":319610,"uid":10894,"like":95,"dislike":7,"score":88,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T07:13:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0abf98e2e8f0cf5af0443cbb58b56959088aff9b","tid":319610,"uid":114097,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T07:51:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係茶記叫左個餐蛋飯,跟住對面有兩個人搭檯<br />\n兩個係度諗食乜,其中一個想叫餐蛋飯,另一個就屌鬼佢,最on9就係食餐蛋飯<br />\n自己整好過啦咁,咁就冇叫<br />\n之後茶仔就放左碟餐蛋飯係我面前<br />\n我望下對面,佢又冇左我兩眼<br />\n之後就沈默左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n琴日我見碟嘢嚟已經知衰<br />\n不過冇諗過你會一早叫咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望你唔好介意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86d79186f80f33b49d6dc70626ed283d9086f871","tid":319610,"uid":25345,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T07:54:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>餐蛋飯要整得好食唔容易<br />\n個鼓油已經係一大學問<br />\n油度甜度色水 要較到完美<br />\n塊餐肉要煎到外脆內juicy 又唔可以太厚<br />\n隻蛋要煎到邊脆 蛋白要幼嫩得黎又唔可以成pat鼻涕咁 蛋黃汁要夠濃而唔係一pat水咁<br />\n個飯基本野 唔講了<br />\n咁先為之一碟正既餐蛋飯</blockquote><br />\n係<br />\n食過正既餐蛋飯<br />\n美食黎<br />\n但多數茶記既係餐肉都冇咩鮮色 霉霉地既餐肉咬落好似咬膠咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c77015697c9913dff781ac4ddd5d973c534ceca","tid":319610,"uid":799,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T07:55:27.000Z","msg":"愈簡單既野愈撚難整呀, 茶記d 太陽蛋, 脆邊, 加甜鼓油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a68ed3055f4f9c82c4e4e21e505c59db8a3fc74f","tid":319610,"uid":48276,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T07:57:31.000Z","msg":"茶記脆脆地都叫個楊洲炒飯啊<br />\n<br />\n餐蛋飯感覺真係好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f8996da7072e86da2d86343a1214da3c2fe152","tid":319610,"uid":17322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T08:00:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d1f86f3e795ead8e7df17978d3b0ce16411f34c7","tid":319610,"uid":12755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T08:08:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>茶記脆脆地都叫個楊洲炒飯啊<br />\n<br />\n餐蛋飯感覺真係好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽講港島區有間望海既餐廳，主打餐蛋飯/面，開左19幾年</blockquote><br />\nLocation ?"},{"pid":"0a1c5e1daecda20dd912f3907e0553064810055b","tid":319610,"uid":17322,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T08:16:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"196a5956ac9e233c73dfe3b2337c851010ac82b6","tid":319610,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T08:26:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f45452052467fc374ffcb037cfff417e8ff6415","tid":319610,"uid":127789,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T08:27:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ec442eb101b12f0ce16d2324d73ed1e0ac4f42","tid":319610,"uid":21871,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T08:41:06.000Z","msg":"餐蛋飯有水準好撚難<br />\n<br />\n比班食開劣食既豬笑你都好正路<br />\n<br />\n因為佢地連擺緊咩入口都唔撚知<br />\n<br />\n太陽蛋脆邊，蛋黃要完整<br />\n<br />\n餐肉要微燶，仲要唔可以太鹹，長城牌一定唔好食<br />\n<br />\n仲有甜鼓油一定要靚<br />\n<br />\n飯都好講究，太硬太軟都唔好食<br />\n<br />\n加條生菜個Ｄ撚樣可以去死"},{"pid":"8028b7262bfc24a98481b5f240db340f0d08f02e","tid":319610,"uid":58889,"like":