nail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F13%2F172342_141e7b4da9554f5d0b42a10e3a2a70fd.jpg&h=1bf4f958&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"99e69ab01ede0f6f313ef895f6d1ae790c0f16d2","tid":319610,"uid":35749,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:25:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>班on9都未見過大蛇屙屎，餐蛋飯先係最顯出師傅功架嘅嘢</blockquote><br />\n上次食過白頭佬整既 舊叉燒同隻蛋再加啲洋蔥 係我呢世食過最好食既叉蛋飯</blockquote><br />\n人地講餐蛋你講咩叉蛋啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話知你食神 9唔搭8"},{"pid":"3baf903a95dff6a510cf5f104efaa49269418e92","tid":319610,"uid":42119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:25:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/video/20130615/392pix/1371242235_f5ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fvideo%2F20130615%2F392pix%2F1371242235_f5ed.jpg&h=1c13053d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好reasonable"},{"pid":"3ad2284b76b7d0cba233fb1d1c0d939bcff9b2c8","tid":319610,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:27:50.000Z","msg":"即該拍抬屌柒佢 再大叫你識條春咩"},{"pid":"ea8795e2dbffd4b61b655c13186139b03b2774e2","tid":319610,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:29:45.000Z","msg":"笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57dbb25d327b00a4ad0c77b543756c19617ed8e1","tid":319610,"uid":2438,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:29:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>餐蛋飯有水準好撚難<br />\n<br />\n比班食開劣食既豬笑你都好正路<br />\n<br />\n因為佢地連擺緊咩入口都唔撚知<br />\n<br />\n太陽蛋脆邊，蛋黃要完整<br />\n<br />\n餐肉要微燶，仲要唔可以太鹹，長城牌一定唔好食<br />\n<br />\n仲有甜鼓油一定要靚<br />\n<br />\n飯都好講究，太硬太軟都唔好食<br />\n<br />\n加條生菜個Ｄ撚樣可以去死</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n潛力潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d67423a053b86cc98d18d0d728a942524725fe2","tid":319610,"uid":14816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:32:20.000Z","msg":"俾個post搞到好想食餐蛋飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d12eb07945b2c878a7397ac9ff4db6423cbdda88","tid":319610,"uid":16827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:36:03.000Z","msg":"又一新潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb5cbbf2bf307d5ff0577e8a55d016ecfac7c5de","tid":319610,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:39:44.000Z","msg":"講餐蛋飯竟然無人提呢間野？！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/13/173941_bdf0e4df85d441611cc8ac1a9a1e34f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F13%2F173941_bdf0e4df85d441611cc8ac1a9a1e34f5.jpg&h=232974e8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/13/173943_76b5e08c73bcb3b0fb2c81854b229928.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F13%2F173943_76b5e08c73bcb3b0fb2c81854b229928.jpg&h=3b9232ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"96a5d117c85b7b035ce0d9590374a9346032cab7","tid":319610,"uid":127944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:42:10.000Z","msg":"好有畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16b32e6aa33ef3ccbb11ceae5f0ee60955eed387","tid":319610,"uid":122601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:42:21.000Z","msg":"如果係平既就無咩所謂，果d 收你40幾$既 真係番去食好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d76bebee1e62ce4955e12caecd26af88a3f3e454","tid":319610,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:44:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>餐蛋飯要整得好食唔容易<br />\n個鼓油已經係一大學問<br />\n油度甜度色水 要較到完美<br />\n塊餐肉要煎到外脆內juicy 又唔可以太厚<br />\n隻蛋要煎到邊脆 蛋白要幼嫩得黎又唔可以成pat鼻涕咁 蛋黃汁要夠濃而唔係一pat水咁<br />\n個飯基本野 唔講了<br />\n咁先為之一碟正既餐蛋飯</blockquote><br />\n問題係餐廳既餐蛋飯無咁好食"},{"pid":"9aed174cebbfb577ae5b008cff057c1160dfd7cf","tid":319610,"uid":77087,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:44:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>茶記脆脆地都叫個楊洲炒飯啊<br />\n<br />\n餐蛋飯感覺真係好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽講港島區有間望海既餐廳，主打餐蛋飯/面，開左19幾年</blockquote><br />\nLocation ?</blockquote><br />\n鯉景灣個頭，沿海個一邊，咩名真係唔知</blockquote><br />\n太興?"},{"pid":"1c952c4f9f63945417222f3a555a27bf4d8026f9","tid":319610,"uid":5497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:47:03.000Z","msg":"餐肉厚切外脆內軟<br />\n濃邊太陽蛋<br />\n豉油汁<br />\n絲苗白飯<br />\n諗起都想食"},{"pid":"6d8e8ff8e8e02eb3888b57c7f5170ce1a7f2a3b5","tid":319610,"uid":20815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:55:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>餐蛋飯要整得好食唔容易<br />\n個鼓油已經係一大學問<br />\n油度甜度色水 要較到完美<br />\n塊餐肉要煎到外脆內juicy 又唔可以太厚<br />\n隻蛋要煎到邊脆 蛋白要幼嫩得黎又唔可以成pat鼻涕咁 蛋黃汁要夠濃而唔係一pat水咁<br />\n個飯基本野 唔講了<br />\n咁先為之一碟正既餐蛋飯</blockquote><br />\n問題係餐廳既餐蛋飯無咁好食</blockquote><br />\n咪係，整到咁好就話啫，整唔到咪求戀期煎鳩熱俾你食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過一間叫濕炒牛河，佢夠膽死蒸熱啲河粉跟住淋啲欠汁加牛肉 就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3179c65e1ed5e8fdfa89956d0f294713cf1f3d3","tid":319610,"uid":69548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:57:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>茶記脆脆地都叫個楊洲炒飯啊<br />\n<br />\n餐蛋飯感覺真係好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽講港島區有間望海既餐廳，主打餐蛋飯/面，開左19幾年</blockquote><br />\nLocation ?</blockquote><br />\n鯉景灣個頭，沿海個一邊，咩名真係唔知</blockquote><br />\n孖沙街果間都幾好食"},{"pid":"419ebfcf6ac8142b981f